QuestData.Title: Seeing Stars
QuestData.Description: You think those naga are good sport, little rabbit?$B$B<Stokalfr chuckles.>$B$BI would savor the chance to do battle with one of those barnacle-crusted behemoths.$B$BIf you want to impress me, bring me the stars from their heads. I might consider you a true $c then.
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect 4 Sea Stars from Elder Trenchwalkers in Azuregale Bay.
